---
const phoneHref = 'tel:+33142365890';
---

<section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1570172619644-dfd03ed5d881?w=1600&q=85"
      alt="Soin visage sur-mesure Paris — Graine de Beauté"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      loading="eager"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#1A1A1A]/45"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <div class="reveal inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/15 backdrop-blur-sm text-white text-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-8 border border-white/20">
        <svg width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
        4.9/5 — Plus de 500 clientes fidèles depuis 2016
      </div>

      <h1 class="reveal reveal-delay-1 text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-white mb-6 leading-tight" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Variable', Georgia, serif; font-weight: 600;">
        Révèle ta beauté<br />
        <em class="text-[#E8D5CC] not-italic">naturelle</em> à Paris
      </h1>

      <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2 text-lg text-white/85 mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
        Chez Graine de Beauté, chaque soin est pensé uniquement pour vous.
        Des soins sur-mesure au cœur du 9e, par des esthéticiennes passionnées qui vous écoutent vraiment.
      </p>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <a
          href="/#contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-[#C9A99A] hover:bg-[#B8897A] text-white font-medium px-8 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors duration-200 text-base"
        >
          Prendre rendez-vous
        </a>
        <a
          href="/services"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center border border-white/50 hover:border-white text-white font-medium px-8 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors duration-200 text-base backdrop-blur-sm"
        >
          Découvrir nos soins
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

